    "text": [
        "Hello John,",
        "I hope you and your family members are doing good during this pandemic situation. I am planning for a trip to Dubai with you in next week to enjoy my vacation.",
        "As you aware of my office environment and busy schedule on task completion for my customer. Last week, I was sick and hospitalized near to my house and doctor analyzed the primary cause for sickness was the mental depression. The doctor strictly informed me to take a break from my work for a couple of weeks. I took this situation to my manager, and he approved my holiday plan.",
        "I have a plan to go to Dubai because of its peaceful environment and many adventurous activities to come out of stress level. As well as I read an article about the future of museum inaugurated in Dubai a month before which is recently added in my vacation plan list.",
        "As I know you very well from my childhood and trustable person in my life. I would like to schedule my trip with you. It will help me out to come out of my depression.",
        "Keep me posting about your schedule so that I will book the tickets and accommodation for our trip.",
        "Take Care,",
        "Bishu"
    ],
